      },
      {
        "author": "Aldrin De Oliveira",
        "stars": 5,
        "text": "Hello, we live in Castro, PR, and we came to visit Bar do Açougueiro da Água Verde for the first time. It was simply awesome, I believe it's one of the best bars in Curitiba. We were well received from the reception, kitchen, and waiters. We were served by Gerson, who literally explained everything about how the bar works. He's simply a great professional and truly embodies the company spirit. He deserves congratulations!!! Finally, we were also served by Jéssica, who treated us very well. Thank you, and we will definitely return!! 👍🤝",
        "date": "27/04/2026",
        "replied": false
      },
      {
        "author": "Gabriel Augusto De Oliveira",
        "stars": 5,
        "text": "Excellent experience, great service, good food, good beer, top-notch atmosphere. Totally worth it. We were served by Gerson and Jessica, 100% service.",
